episodes.title: New Years Eve with Johnathan Lawhorne
episodes.description: Is Meredith OK you guys? Friend of the podcast Johnathan Lawhorne joins me to try to figure that out, and we wrap up 2025 with a recap of Stacey Rusch's rise to reality tv fame (a Vanity Fair call out?!), that Mary Cosby cult documentary, pepper spray Tok, Nicki Minaj's predictable MAGA rebrand and a lot more.
